snippet.title: Star Ocean The Divine Force - State of Play Oct 2021 Debut Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Star Ocean 25th Anniversary commemorative product.
Square Enix and developer Tri-Ace present the latest title in the Star Ocean RPG series.

Featuring a story that blends fantasy and a sci-fi settings, a plethora of different playable characters and side stories, and a unique battle system that allows for thrilling fights using simple and instinctive controls.

Due for release in 2022
Watch out for future updates!
